{"tid":2209861,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"19解放軍機再越線 陸恐嚇鏟除蔡英文 台警告懸崖勒馬  兩岸戰火一觸即發","createTime":"2020-09-20T03:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T04:33:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03a2e066758a3359ec9b74abf6da98d35f2e1262","tid":2209861,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/Q3HTHANMPJBUPN6JPYI353MRP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FQ3HTHANMPJBUPN6JPYI353MRP4%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=938b5592\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200920%2FQ3HTHANMPJBUPN6JPYI353MRP4%2F&h=78989961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200920/Q3HTHANMPJBUPN6JPYI353MRP4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n19解放軍機再越線 陸恐嚇鏟除蔡英文 台警告懸崖勒馬 <br />\n兩岸戰火一觸即發<br />\n<br />\n台海正陷入最危險時刻！美國國務次卿克拉奇訪台期間，大陸先後於18、19日派出十多架軍機穿海峽中線，加劇兩岸緊張局勢；《環球時報》在Twitter撥火：「如蔡英文有任何舉動觸犯了（大陸的）《反分裂國家法》，戰爭將會點燃，蔡也將被鏟除」，火藥味濃。對此，台灣國防部表達嚴正譴責，「並呼籲大陸當局自制，懸崖勒馬」。美國國防部發言人亦稱，解放軍的侵略性與破壞性回應，反映中國正不斷企圖改變現狀與改寫歷史。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：專家：三大侵略手段 危機波及全球<br />\n<br />\n解放軍繼前日派出18架戰機擾台，昨日上午7時又派出19架戰機擾台，。。。。。。。。。。。，影響我飛行安全，立即迴轉脫離，一切後果自負！」驅逐言語顯然比以往強硬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-h6-7CGPu9jHou-wuhOdtsspDTc=/3368x1667/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RMRPGQGIWJAO3DZ7YBWWMKCZGU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-h6-7CGPu9jHou-wuhOdtsspDTc%3D%2F3368x1667%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRMRPGQGIWJAO3DZ7YBWWMKCZGU.gif&h=693fcd94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n解放軍模擬炸美軍基地<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，中共喉舌《環球時報》昨在Twitter以英文寫道：「台灣領導人蔡英文與訪台的美國高官晉餐，顯然在玩火。。。。。。。。。。。。。，那麼解放軍即可展開毀滅式打擊，也恐嚇道「（蔡英文當局）他們或者懸崖勒馬，或者跌入深淵，粉身碎骨。」<br />\n<br />\n面對北京文攻武嚇，台灣國防安全研究院國防資源與產業研究所長蘇紫雲向《蘋果》指出，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，因中共文化向來都是七分政治、三分軍事，解放軍其實是自己口中的紙老虎。」<br />\n<br />\n蘇紫雲認為，當下美國跟日本的高官都在台灣，共軍擾台 的舉動，。。。。。。。。。。。。，解放軍空軍昨更在微博首次發佈戰略轟炸機「轟6K」模擬轟炸美軍關島基地的畫面，極具挑釁性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bH6ayf2x6V2-N0iIA_JlfOvcIBs=/1080x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5KWHYSN72FHBZP4IBWSVPCBLYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbH6ayf2x6V2-N0iIA_JlfOvcIBs%3D%2F1080x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5KWHYSN72FHBZP4IBWSVPCBLYI.jpg&h=5afc0628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國國家主席習近平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pKlpYB5mK2Z8dARhX61nA0kO-vw=/992x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WD2SDSHKWFAR5J24JWISNAES7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpKlpYB5mK2Z8dARhX61nA0kO-vw%3D%2F992x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWD2SDSHKWFAR5J24JWISNAES7E.jpg&h=64247c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣總統蔡英文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析︰虛張聲勢擺姿態<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹向本報分析，大陸有見台美關係越走越近，未有任何具體反擊行動，而此刻開戰無利於中共領導人習近平，《環時》只是「虛張聲勢」，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。例：「德國二戰吞併波蘭之時，軍力亦未必勝過英國及法國；日本在太平洋開戰時，國力更比不上美國。」最後德國就是靠逐個擊破，以戰養戰助大勢力。<br />\n<br />\n在當下世界格局中，兩岸的角力反映出民主體制對抗威權體制的脈絡。。。。。。。。。。。。。，而北京目前也沒有辦法阻止台灣與國際的聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/台灣國防部"},{"pid":"d3b0158e67f0077643469be8b9d33b31717ea742","tid":2209861,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"未必係專登既 支那製gps有幾準大家都知"},{"pid":"f486b60558a558867435b3582079df77e37eca62","tid":2209861,"uid":9694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"你地打啦屌你<br />\n你敢打我切呀"},{"pid":"381f87bfdd8640a2a275c01ae72ffae2d4ff50cd","tid":2209861,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b0158e67f0077643469be8b9d33b31717ea742","tid":2209861,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"未必係專登既 支那製gps有幾準大家都知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"戰略武器都可以跌左兩支係自己入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbe9ea617ed686d2843883ed3dea61cce0f9aec","tid":2209861,"uid":218407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"本人多次立下毒誓 約可開戰成功 勢必含屎裸跑維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c141e4be12246d383677edff0feacdd97788f277","tid":2209861,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"蒼蠅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小心比人拍死"}]}